		<h2>The conference for participants</h2>
		<p>
		For more than a decade, the OT Conference has been the place where Europe’s leading
		software development practitioners gather to share their latest thinking.
		</p><p>
		Don't expect to spend hours listening to interminable speeches. OT2004 is for people
		that want to share experiences, work together to address hot topics, and ask tough
		questions. Most sessions stress participation and learning - you don't need to know
		the answers to join in, you just need enthusiasm.
		</p><p>
		Come prepared to spend four days taking part in an exchange of experiences and ideas
		that will bring benefit to you and your organisation. Test your ideas with people who
		have no axe to grind and lots of experience to share.
		</p><p>
		Whether you're interested in the latest technology, pioneering development practices
		or innovative project management techniques OT2004 has something valuable to offer
		you.
		</p>
